entry.title: [PULL] Wallet Private Key Encryption Take 3
entry.summary: The Bitcoin repository on Github has recently seen a pull request from Matt, which rebases onto the wallet class and is ready for "wtf is this crap" messages. The link to the pull request is available for anyone who wants to see the details. However, there is no further information provided in the context about the nature of the changes or the potential impact of the pull request.
